1. **Plan-Level Optimization:** Identified wrong execution strategy (full scan instead of indexed lookup)
2. **Pre-Built Index Usage:** Leveraged existing `orders_orderkey_hash` index from Storage Guide
3. **Reduced I/O:** Changed from scanning 15M rows to loading only 1 index + 1 column
